@startuml
start
:系统上电/重启;
:初始化外设与数据;
while (主循环) is (true)
  fork
    :PCProcess() - 处理串口1;
  fork again
    :Rs485Process() - 处理RS485;
  fork again
    :G4GProcess() - 处理4G收发;
  fork again
    :QRProcess() - 处理二维码;
  end fork
endwhile
stop

' QRProcess 细节

note right
QRProcess:
 - 复制接收数据
 - ExtractValidData_Bytes -> valid_data
 - IsCvjFormat ?
 - 若是 -> 根据 Cmd 分发 DoCmd1..DoCmd6
 - 否 -> 上报失败
end note

@enduml